94
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:23,840
Step number two, set up a landing page.

95
00:05:23,840 --> 00:05:25,520
Do some basic SEO research.

96
00:05:25,520 --> 00:05:28,080
Go to hrefs or go to any free SEO tool.

97
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:30,639
